@base = http://localhost:8000
@agent = agentreg:acme.example:procurement-review

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Registry metadata
GET {{base}}/registry

### Resolve canonical agent
GET {{base}}/agents/{{agent}}

### Current lifecycle status
GET {{base}}/agents/{{agent}}/status

### Resolve alias
GET {{base}}/aliases/acme:procurement-review

### Authority allow
POST {{base}}/authority/evaluate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "authority": {"status":"active","actions":["procurement.review"],"maximum_value":10000},
  "request": {"agent":"agentreg:acme.example:procurement-review","action":"procurement.review","value":2500}
}

### Events
GET {{base}}/events
